==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-əʊldə(r)|-əʊldə(r)]]

===Noun===
'''shoulder''' (''plural:'' '''[[shoulders]]''')
# (anatomy): One side of the top of the [[torso]], where an [[arm]] attaches or joins
# A part of a [[road]] used to stop on in emergencies
#:''He stopped the car on the [[shoulder]] of the highway to change the flat tire.''

